  "2026-07-22T05:17:51.297Z",codex-root,"Migrated four changelog categories to when.labels with preserved semver increments, replaced skip-changelog with pre-exclude, added explicit breaking-change major resolution, and retained default patch resolution. Full local release gates pass at 100/100/100/100 coverage."
