learnings[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T05:15:40.549Z",codex-root,A successful GitHub check can still carry actionable deprecation annotations; exact-head annotation inspection is required.
  "2026-07-22T05:17:52.498Z",codex-root,"Default patch resolution is represented by a final version-resolver category without a when predicate; specific breaking-change major resolution precedes it, while changelog categories carry minor/patch increments directly."
