close_reason: Migrated Release Drafter classification syntax while preserving grouping and version resolution.
body: "## Problem\n\nMerged-head Release Draft run `29893136465` succeeded but emitted five deprecation annotations. The configuration still uses legacy `categories[*].labels` and top-level `exclude-labels`, which Release Drafter will remove.\n\n## Source\n\nRelease Drafter PR 1558 is the authoritative migration guide. It moves category predicates under `when`, replaces top-level excludes with a `type: pre-exclude` category, and represents version resolution through category `semver-increment` plus `type: version-resolver` entries.\n\n## Scope\n\nMigrate `.github/release-drafter.yml` without changing generated category grouping or version-bump semantics. Verify repository workflows, YAML parsing, local release gates, PR checks, bot review, and a merged-head Release Draft run with zero annotations."
